== Prerequisite

In order to build Flint's Java code base, you need Apache Ant or NetBeans.


== How to build flint.jar

We use Apache Ant in order to build it on command line.
For creating flint.jar:
$ cd flint
$ ant jar


== How to launch flint.jar

You need JRE 1.7 or later in order to run Flint.
For launching it from command line:
$ java -jar flint.jar [argument ...]
